Introduction

Lee Seoryoung (이서령) was the leader and main vocalist of the girl group GWSN, also known as Girls in the Park, under The Wave Music. She was introduced as a GWSN member in 2018 and debuted with the group on September 5 of the same year with their first album, "The Park in the Night Part One". During 2018, Seoryoung collaborated with Highlight's Dongwoon for a single called "Color Me".

In addition to her role as a singer, she showcases her versatility by demonstrating a talent for singing trot and playing the guitar.
